  "onboardingPlaceBody": "We use this to label the place Lighthouse learns first. It does not change how the app behaves; you can skip it.",
  "onboardingWifiTitle": "Learn words for each place",
  "onboardingWifiBody": "Lighthouse can use your Wi-Fi network name, scrambled on this device, to learn which words your child needs in different places like home and school. The name never leaves the tablet, and this is optional.",
